till point to major opportunities on the other side._\n\nThe headline indices have barely flinched during this pullback, which makes the selling pressure underneath them easy to underestimate. As of Friday‚Äôs close, the Dow was only 4.18% off its highs. The S&P 500 was down 4.61%. Even the Nasdaq‚Äîhome to the most momentum-heavy names‚Äîwas ‚Äúonly‚Äù off 6.55%.\n\nBut that doesn‚Äôt tell the real story.\n\nThe¬†**median S&P 500 stock**¬†is down¬†_almost 16%_¬†from its recent high, as Mike Zaccardi, CFA, CMT points out¬†[here](https://x.com/MikeZaccardi/status/1992245804027764814?s=20).\n\nTwitter Embed\n\n[Visit this post on X](https://twitter.com/MikeZaccardi/status/1992245804027764814?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1992245804027764814%7Ctwgr%5E9c2764dfed9dd6de46a670b377e9ed183ad253c0%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zerohedge.com%2Fnews%2F2025-11-24%2Fmarket-pullback-has-been-worse-it-looks)\n\n[![](https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1033689747884060673/fgYgkSvu_normal.jpg)](https://twitter.com/MikeZaccardi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1992245804027764814%7Ctwgr%5E9c2764dfed9dd6de46a670b377e9ed183ad253c0%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zerohedge.com%2Fnews%2F2025-11-24%2Fmarket-pullback-has-been-worse-it-looks)\n\n[Mike Zaccardi, CFA, CMT ![üçñ](https://abs-0.twimg.com/emoji/v2/svg/1f356.svg)](https://twitter.com/MikeZaccardi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1992245804027764814%7Ctwgr%5E9c2764dfed9dd6de46a670b377e9ed183ad253c0%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zerohedge.com%2Fnews%2F2025-11-24%2Fmarket-pullback-has-been-worse-it-looks)\n\n[@MikeZaccardi](https://twitter.com/MikeZaccardi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1992245804027764814%7Ctwgr%5E9c2764dfed9dd6de46a670b377e9ed183ad253c0%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zerohedge.com%2Fnews%2F2025-11-24%2Fmarket-pullback-has-been-worse-it-looks)\n\n¬∑\n\n[Follow](https://twitter.com/intent/follow